cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the limitations of traditional reinforcement learning in achieving AGI, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of real numbers in reinforcement learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper proposes possible alterations to traditional reinforcement learning, which is a topic in multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and neural networks (cs.NE).
